thothbot.parallax.core.shared.math

Class Matrix3

  • java.lang.Object
    • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.math.Matrix3

  • public class Matrix3
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements three-dimensional matrix. MxM, where M=3. This matrix actually is array which is represented the following indexes: 
     
 0 3 6
 1 4 7
 2 5 8
    Author:
    thothbot
